title: Frontend Developer (React.js)
description: We're looking for a skilled Frontend Developer to build responsive and modern web interfaces using React.js and Tailwind CSS. The ideal candidate should have experience with REST APIs, state management, and responsive design.

title: Mobile App Developer (Flutter)
description: We need a Flutter Developer to build cross-platform mobile applications for Android and iOS. You’ll work closely with designers and backend engineers to deliver pixel-perfect and smooth user experiences.
